Stephen W. Burns https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephen_W._Burns 0 Stephen W. Burns (November 15, 1954 – February 22, 1990; also credited as Stephan W. Burns and Stephan Burns) was an American actor best known for playing Pete Stancheck in Herbie Goes Bananas and Jack Cleary in the miniseries The Thorn Birds.
